<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="title">Order Confirmation</h1>
        <div class="content">
            <h2 class="subtitle">Dear Customer,</h2>
            <p>Thank you for placing your order with us. Here are the details of your order:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Burger:</strong> {{order.burger.name}}</li>
                <li><img src="{{order.burger.image}}" alt="{{order.burger.name}} Image" class="image is-64x64">
                <li><strong>Delivery Personnel:</strong> {{order.spacemonkey.name}}</li>
                <li><img src="{{order.spacemonkey.image}}" alt="{{order.spacemonkey.name}} Image"
                        class="image is-64x64">
                <li><strong>Order ID:</strong> #42069{{order.id}}</li>
                <li><strong>Order Placed On:</strong> {{format_date order.createdAt}}</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Your order is currently being prepared and will be on its way soon. You can track the progress of your
                order by clicking on the "Track My Order" button below.</p>
            <button class="button is-primary" onclick="window.location.href='/orders/tracking'">Track My Order</button>
        </div>
        <p>Here is your order's QR code:</p>
        <div id="qrcode-container"></div>
    </div>
</section>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/qrcodejs/1.0.0/qrcode.min.js"></script>
<script>
    new QRCode(document.getElementById("qrcode-container"), {
        text: window.location.href,
        width: 128,
        height: 128
    });
</script>
